{"tid":1177353,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"失戀既入晒黎聽歌","createTime":"2019-05-29T18:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T14:49:25.000Z","uid":221104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3787ad8b2536e00797df1448ebc8994d47a2b157","tid":1177353,"uid":221104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:10:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lmE6wxztzR8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlmE6wxztzR8&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=919471f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lmE6wxztzR8</a><br />\n<br />\n學習下：<br />\n<br />\nHow to forgive yourself <br />\n<br />\n連自己都唔原諒、<br />\n連自己都唔愛、<br />\n又好難怪對方拋棄自己。<br />\n<br />\n過來人，<br />\n我明既，您有壓力我有壓力，<br />\n我都曾經壓力爆煲過，<br />\n家家有本難念的經，<br />\n一家唔知一家事。<br />\n<br />\n但如果真係好唔開心既，<br />\n就同公司請個長大假，<br />\n坐國泰飛出國散下心，<br />\n最好去大自然地區散心，<br />\n日本又好台灣又好泰國邊度都好，<br />\n齊齊整整安全去完返黎又係一條好漢/好女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錢既，<br />\n香港都大把郊野公園或大自然地方唔洗錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緣份有聚散，有人隨行已是幸運；<br />\n人心有冷暖，有人懂得便是幸福。<br />\n<br />\n有緣起，就有緣滅；<br />\n拎得起，要學習學得低。<br />\n<br />\n──懂得滿足，幸福駐足<br />\n　　尼采曾經說道︰<br />\n「對於平凡人來說，平凡和簡單就是幸福。」<br />\n<br />\n祝各位正在失落失戀失意的人，<br />\n早日振作起來，重拾對自己的信心，<br />\n自強者打不倒，自棄者扶不起。<br />\n<br />\n努力💪🏻加油，希望您們都早日解脫心魔，<br />\n振翅高飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一起努力，成為更好的自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b025ef59f1f47b2ed20faf0e7d8a4f7bb2bb088b","tid":1177353,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:12:57.000Z","msg":"香港終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=7812189b\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a>"},{"pid":"e0679789811f2ac398171a3e5e163250343b951e","tid":1177353,"uid":190811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"無人陪我去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb3c0778a130d9d4e4da95aab0689411bb81a4e","tid":1177353,"uid":221104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0679789811f2ac398171a3e5e163250343b951e","tid":1177353,"uid":190811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"無人陪我去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"巴打洗咩人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係自己一個去日本"}]}